      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "SPRING SIGNAL (1) was strong over this course and distance last time despite filling the minors, finishing 3.5 lengths behind Faith In Caeden in 18.66 and recording a new PB here. Going well and rates on top. BARSTOOL DOLLARS (8) produced a modest effort most recently when seventh at this track over 320m behind Muscle Memory (18.73) in a Grade 4/5. Placed at her previous run. Strong form has emerged from her last run. Should be about the money. TERESA'S ANGEL (2) finds it hard to break through. Has been in the minors the last two runs, the latest finishing third (18.37) at this track. Solid record here at the distance winning two races. Strong form has emerged from her last run. Expected to be in the finish again. CHRISY'S WISH (6) won by a wide margin last start. Big chance on that form.",
